力而停低時  <br />\n好多時會見到交通警在場協助, 直至拖車將車拖走<br />\n而佢地唔會因為咁而發告票, 又或者可能只有阻街, 但冇阻路呢條例<br />\n<br />\n但呢單案個 case, 其實係佢一係抄晒成條街既<br />\n車, 而家抄一架唔抄其他, 咁就變成咗有欠公平,<br />\n而且當佢所有轆都拆走晒時, 佢又重算唔算一架車,<br />\n發告票又是否正確做法 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aec279aba2ad7e6be806d38d07bc85ccc7eda69d","tid":1187367,"uid":124655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"000bc406730bfd903f6e9a477a5d1dd7c9c2af04","tid":1187367,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T15:43:46.000Z","msg":"霑叔個女都唔俾面"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T15:47:57.000Z","msg":"霑叔個女坐開港鐵 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20181122/mobile/bkn-20181122234521341-1122_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20181122%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20181122234521341-1122_00862_001.html&d=HGsIALD6rBmJFWdd%2FklElmlQkZRBUTTGMtnLt8L03NM%3D&h=b08a0732\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20181122/mobile/bkn-20181122234521341-1122_00862_001.html</a>"}]}